#####Configure data selection for Windows

1. Start a PowerShell session.
2. Navigate to the Edge System installation directory: %Program Files% /OSIsoft/EdgeSystem.
3. To configure data selection, do one of the following:
   * Type in the properties and their values through a command as shown in this example:
   
   ...
.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSelection Selected=true UnitId=1 RegisterType=3 RegisterOffset=12 DataTypeCode=10 ScanRate=2000
   ...

   * Import a .json file through a command as shown in this example:

   ...
.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSelection import SampleFilePath/SampleConfigurations.json
   ...
   
4. To view configured data selection, run command

   ...
.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSelection
   ...

